{"tid":1603128,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新疆集中營建地下鐵籠虐犯","createTime":"2019-09-29T15:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T15:27:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"33bc4caad321082fd7e2730f1f338d13f4c083e8","tid":1603128,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20190928/XGQ46NLSI37T3CWBXSBB65XNCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20190928%2FXGQ46NLSI37T3CWBXSBB65XNCQ%2F&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrc22uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=fcc1a2c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20190928%2FXGQ46NLSI37T3CWBXSBB65XNCQ%2F&h=2841db76\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20190928/XGQ46NLSI37T3CWBXSBB65XNCQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n新疆集中營建地下鐵籠虐犯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/fBXs_F0JnPim6A8jR3XzKWAA8sI=/190x98/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/ZGD3QJ6NGUZ2JDQVXG2IYZVSEI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FfBXs_F0JnPim6A8jR3XzKWAA8sI%3D%2F190x98%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FZGD3QJ6NGUZ2JDQVXG2IYZVSEI.gif&h=67d7d8e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共在新疆以職業培訓之名開「再教育營」（圖），大規模關押維族和其他穆斯林進行強制洗腦，其中兩名哈薩克族獲釋者近日對自由亞洲電台指證，聲稱他們曾被關在深達20米的地下鐵籠，宛如鳥獸，有人被迫接種不知名疫苗；即使有幸重見天日，但兩人都出現嚴重健康問題，盼國際社會關注維人在新疆的慘況。<br />\n<br />\n被迫接種不知名疫苗<br />\n<br />\n現年31歲的受害者葉兒哈利．葉兒滅可原籍新疆伊犁，已移民哈薩克，在哈國從事邊境貿易，2017年11月9日入境中國被抓捕。當局指他曾在當地清真寺做伊瑪目（領禱人）、非法使用WhatsApp通訊工具；他被戴上手銬腳鏈、黑頭套，押在老虎椅上被迫吸煙及喝酒（穆斯林不煙酒）；一周後送入伊寧市監獄，遭拷打逼認罪，每天只能吃一塊饅頭一杯水。一周後又把他轉到霍城縣集中營，即官方所稱「培訓中心」。<br />\n<br />\n另一位獲釋者圖爾孫別克．哈利來自新疆額敏縣，也已移民哈國，做邊貿生意。2017年9月入境時被捕，理由和葉兒哈利相似。他被羈押在額敏縣一座新建再教育營地下室。「在地下20米深處，有很多房間，每間約10平方米，每房有六個鐵籠子，每個鐵籠關押一人，鐵籠子很小，一平米左右，人進去很擠。」他指在鐵籠裏無法睡覺，只能坐着。看守員拿鐵棍，看誰睡就打醒。他又稱有囚犯被強行注射接種不知名的疫苗，也有人失去生育能力。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台"},{"pid":"0926985b867209ed8a73ee7e91585711e0720ff0","tid":1603128,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:18:47.000Z","msg":"細菌實驗"},{"pid":"9fab0c91b363879482568cd2810d450a28e74928","tid":1603128,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:20:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">前&hearts;線&hearts;B&hearts;B&hearts;需&hearts;要&hearts;你</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WEddZM3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWEddZM3.jpg&h=f62ae3bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03428ebb4e1d4d36faaa133b2bd9196de4f99c85","tid":1603128,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:20:38.000Z","msg":"虐囚，犯咩？有咩罪"},{"pid":"3b183b1381c08261a6e3a9d05967fdfd52d84d5a","tid":1603128,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:22:34.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768e560609a1dbd1805f00ab4a9bd0feec58e2b0","tid":1603128,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"03428ebb4e1d4d36faaa133b2bd9196de4f99c85","tid":1603128,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:20:38.000Z","msg":"虐囚，犯咩？有咩罪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"原罪, 出生喺支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec786c2c27b7fd86086b9137d556457e1f38458f","tid":1603128,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"#法律知識<br />\n<br />\n警方可以根據警隊條例54(1)對任何行動可疑的人，或54(2)對任何有合理懷疑已犯法的人進行截查。<br />\n<br />\n若你被無理截查，本頻道建議直接引用法律條文質問警方：<br />\n✅根據哪一條警隊條例進行截查；<br />\n✅如果回答54(1)，可追問警方為何你行動可疑；<br />\n✅如果回答54(2)，請追問警方為何懷疑你已經或準備犯法。<br />\n<br />\n案例指出警方應根據客觀事實（時間、地點、現場情況、行為等）作主觀判斷。<br />\n<br />\n‼️截查期間，警方不能要求你解鎖或關閉手機。"},{"pid":"00170cd1e2e55bad253d81e4a26f3abf71d316c2","tid":1603128,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:27:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他又稱有囚犯被強行注射接種不知名的疫苗，也有人失去生育能力。</span></span></strong>"}]}